appearance(black, "the absence of light -- the darkness of a moonless night").
appearance(blue, "a cool, calm colour -- the shade of a clear daytime sky and of deep, still water").
appearance(forest, "tall trees crowded together, green light filtering through the leaves onto a floor of moss and fallen branches").
appearance(green, "a fresh, restful colour -- the shade of grass and of new spring leaves").
appearance(ocean, "a vast expanse of blue-green water reaching to the horizon, its surface forever moving in waves").
appearance(orange, "a warm, glowing colour between red and yellow -- the shade of a sunset and of its namesake fruit").
appearance(purple, "a deep, rich colour between blue and red -- the shade of plums and of twilight").
appearance(rainbow, "a wide arc of colour -- red, orange, yellow, green, blue, and violet -- that appears when sunlight shines through rain").
appearance(red, "a warm, intense colour -- the shade of fire, of ripe strawberries, and of blood").
appearance(snow, "soft white flakes that settle into a smooth, bright blanket covering everything in quiet").
appearance(sunrise, "the dark sky brightens with soft gold and rose as the sun edges over the horizon and daylight returns").
appearance(sunset, "the sky glows in bands of orange, pink, and deep red as the sun sinks below the horizon and the light slowly fades into dusk").
appearance(white, "the presence of all colours of light together -- the brightness of fresh snow").
appearance(yellow, "a bright, cheerful colour -- the shade of the midday sun and of ripe lemons").
